<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>This section may <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Guide_to_writing_better_articles#Stay_on_topic" title="Wikipedia:Guide to writing better articles" class="mw-redirect">stray from the topic</a> of the article</b>&#160;into the topic of another article, <i><a href="/wiki/Teletraffic_engineering" title="Teletraffic engineering">teletraffic engineering</a></i>. Please help <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Traffic_shaping&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Traffic_shaping&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this section</a> or discuss this issue on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Traffic_shaping" title="Talk:Traffic shaping">talk page</a>.</td>
